    <!-- Initial Wizard -->
    <string name="step1_description">Coming Home works with your Nest Thermostat to automatically set the status to home or away.\n
    \nYour first step will be to use the \'Connect to Nest\' button to grant Coming Home permission to
    check and set status on Nest.</string>
    <string name="step2_description">After you have connected to Nest, use the \'At Home\' button to set the geo location of your home.\n
    \nComing Home will set a geofence that will trigger when you leave or arrive and will automatically
    set the away or home status for Nest.</string>
